`,n.jsx(e.h2,{children:"About the Institute"}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"IIIT Raichur operates in Raichur, Karnataka, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning AI/ML and data, Cybersecurity, Computer vision and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across top public tech institutes, anchor your choices with labs, facilities, and sponsored work rather than brand alone."}),`
