`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"If you have limited time, prioritize three moves: (1) shortlist labs and write lab-specific pitches; (2) ship one fresh artifact or small reproduction per target lab; (3) prepare logistics (NOC, hostel plan, travel) so you can accept quickly. These three steps alone raise conversion dramatically versus generic CV blasts."}),`
`,n.jsx(e.h2,{children:"About the Institute"}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"IIT (ISM) Dhanbad operates in Dhanbad, Jharkhand, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning Mining and earth sciences, Geospatial and remote sensing, Energy and sustainability and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across the IIT system, anchor your choices with the IIT internships hub to see where this institute leads on depth, facilities, and sponsored work."}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"Because the institute is embedded in Dhanbad, interns can tap into nearby industry partners, field sites, and alumni-led startups. This often translates to problem statements with real datasets or hardware constraints rather than purely academic exercises."}),`
