`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"NIT Agartala operates in Agartala, Tripura, giving interns access to regional industries and research ecosystems. The campus hosts active centers spanning Electrical and power, Computer science and AI, Electronics and communications and collaborates with government and industry sponsors. If you are comparing across top public tech institutes, anchor your choices with labs, facilities, and sponsored work rather than brand alone."}),`
